===Letter===
{{head|ru|letter|lower case||upper case|Э}}

# The thirty-first letter of the Russian [[Cyrillic]] alphabet. Its name is {{l|ru|э|tr=ɛ}} or {{l|ru|э оборотное|tr=ɛ oborótnoje|t=backwards ɛ}} and it has the broad sound of {{IPAchar|/e/}}. Unlike {{l|ru|е}}, it is not pronounced with a preceding {{IPAchar|/j/}} sound or a palatalized consonant. It is preceded by [[ь|Ь]] and followed by [[ю|Ю]].

